creator: Various
description:
Librivox recording of Astounding Stories of Super-Science, October 1930
Read by LibriVox Volunteers.

Issue no. 10 of the magazine brings you Stolen Brains by Captain S.P. Meek
The Invisible Death by Victor Rousseau
Prisoners on the Electron by Robert H. Leitfred
Producing Heat by Artic Cold
Part 2 of Jetta of the Lowlands by Ray Cummings
An Extra Man by Jackson Gee along with  the Readers' Corner and interesting scientific facts (Summary by Annise)

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audiobooks, or to become a volunteer reader, please visit librivox.org.
